high_descs: Turn around so your back is to the refrigerator, walk to the cabinet with the metal top.
Pick up the knife from the cabinet.
Turn left, turn left, turn left, walk toward the wall, turn to face the stove.
Slice the potato that is on the counter to the right of the stove.
Put the knife on the counter.
Pick up one of the potato slices.
Turn left, walk forward and past the table, turn left, walk to the refrigerator, turn right, walk to the double sink.
Put the potato in the left-hand sink and fill the sink with water.
Take the potato from the sink and turn completely around  clockwise so you face the sinks again.
Place the potato slice in front of the left hand sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed potato slice in front of a sink.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the counter to the left of the oven.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn right, go forward, turn left at the counter to the right of the oven.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Put the knife on the counter.
Take a slice of potato from the counter.
Turn left, go forward, turn left after passing the oven, go forward to the fridge, turn right to the sink.
Wash the potato in the sink, take the potato from the sink.
Move a step to the left and back from the sink.
Put the potato slice on the front edge of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed slice of potato on the edge of a sink.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the counter.
Pick the butter knife up off of the counter.
Turn to the right, walk to the end of the counter.
Slice the potato on the counter.
Put the butter knife next to the sliced potato.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn to the left, go to the sink.
Wash the potato slice in the sink.
Take a step to the left of the sink.
Place the potato slice next to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean slice of potato next to the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter.
Pick up the butter knife that's on the table.
Turn around and take a half a step then turn left and walk to the wall then turn left.
Cut the potato that's to the right of the stove into slices.
Put the knife on the potato slices.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn left and walk until you're even with the fridge to your left then turn left and walk to the fridge and turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the slice of potato in the sink and shut off the water after.
Back up a half step.
Put the slice of potato on the edge of the counter in front of the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean slice of potato on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the counter.
Pick up the butter knife on the left side of the counter.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the oven.
Cut up the potato on the counter to the right of the oven.
Put the knife onto the counter to the left of the potato.
Pick up a piece of sliced potato.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then turn left again and walk over to the sink.
Put the potato slice in the left sink basin, then turn the water on, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean potato slice.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and take a step forward, then turn right to face the counter.
Place the potato slice on the front edge of the counter in front of the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean potato slice on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter.
Pick the knife up from the counter.
Cross the room and turn to face the stove.
Slice the potato on the counter.
Put the knife on the counter.
Take a piece of potato.
Cross the room and stand in front of the sink.
Put the potato in the sink, turn the water on and then off an pick up the potato slice.
Turn around and back up from the sink.
Put the potato slice down on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean potato slice on the counter.
